link: Antti Karttunen, Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..8191
program: (define (sum_A000027_times_elements_in nums) (let loop ((s 0) (nums nums) (i 1)) (cond ((null? nums) s) (else (loop (+ s (* (car nums) i)) (cdr nums) (+ 1 i))))))
